      *   LAST RCV,SCHEDULE DATA
      *===============================================================
     C           ##LAST    BEGSR
     C                     Z-ADDBBTOKU    K$TOKU  40
     C                     Z-ADDBBNONY    K$NONY  40       DELIVERY CODE
