**  ER  (ERROR MESSAGE )
E-01 INPUT ISSUE DATE
E-02 ISSUE DATE ISN'T RIGHT
E-03 DATE TIME ERROR  START > EXIT
E-04 KANBAN KIND ERROR (BLANK , A , B )
E-05 PUBLICATION KIND ERROR (BLANK , 1 , 2 )
E-06 THERE ISN'T APPLICABLE DATA.
E-07 THE FIRST DATA.
E-08 THE LAST DATA.
